{"id":291603,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-西安西万公路丰裕口路段遭村民堵塞抗议/","date":"2013-05-02T09:46:05Z","modified":"2013-05-02T09:46:05Z","title":"维权网 | 西安西万公路丰裕口路段遭村民堵塞抗议拆迁（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span><span></span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span>2013</span></span><span><span>年</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span></span><span><span>月</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></span><span><span>日早上</span></span><span><span>，西安市环山公路周边大量村民因为对韩国三星项目拆迁政策不满，将去往沣峪口的西万公路和进山的路堵塞，因为节日期间许多西安市民自驾车去山边休闲，造成从西万路到沣峪口沿线大堵车。</span></span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span>为了三星项目落地，西安地方政府的力度令人叹为观止，为项目付出</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span></span><span><span>亿，包括对项目进行巨额财政补贴、“</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span></span><span><span>免</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span></span><span><span>减半”所得税优惠、项目运行补贴、土地及建筑无偿提供，并为项目修建高速公路、地铁等交通设施和生活配套等。但是对待土地拆迁的农民，一亩地只给</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30800</span></span><span><span>的补偿，搬迁补偿</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span></span><span><span>万，而且还是只先发</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span></span><span><span>万，剩下的</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span></span><span><span>万</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span></span><span><span>年后再发。</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span>当地农民表示坚决反对政府拟定的拆迁征地政策，反对政府低价购买土地和房屋，反对村长村民代表</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&#8220;</span></span><span><span>捞钱</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&#8220;</span></span><span><span>，希望重新选举村长和村民代表，说他们现在就知道捞钱，到时候带来的污染废气是无法用钱买的。</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span>当地农民曾经多次将周边公路堵塞，表达抗议。</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span><span><br /></span></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http